---
title: Caribbean Lamb & Coconut Sauce with Roast Veggie Toss
description: There’s nothing better than lamb rump that’s juicy on the inside and wonderfully roasted with mild spices on the outside. That’s how
we’re preparing our protein tonight, plus add a drizzle of creamy Caribbean coconut sauce to double down on all that flavour. Delish!

